*************
compiling the program
*************
Simply type 'make' into the terminal and the program will compile.

*************
running the program
*************
from the programs main directory, type './src/A2' to run

Type any message into the terminal and press enter once you've entered it.

Type '-help' at anytime to get instructions

To enter morsecode, make sure there are two spaces between words and you use only
'.' and '-'. There should be a space between each morsecode character

*********
known limitations
********

if attempting to enter morsecode, syntax must adhear exactly

Be mindful of warnings that pop up in the top left corner, they are easy to miss.


